events.title: Genesis
events.subtitle: The annual workshop for freshmen at Astra Robotics
events.content: Our annual workshop for the freshmen that serves as a platform to kindle their interest in Robotics. Various topics in Robotics are introduced that build a foundation for them to explore further. The workshop is structured for students to learn through hands-on-experience by building a bot combining multiple domains of Robotics.

data: Serving as faculty member since 1992, in Mechanical Engineering Department, NIT, Tiruchirappalli-15,
Mechanization of the ringing of Church bell at M/s St. Joseph College Church, Trichy-2 in the year 2000 using ABB DTC drive.
Performance evaluation of reciprocating compressors installed at SSTP, BHEL, Trichy-14.in the year 2004.

Under the center of excellence scheme established calibration facilities for calibration of temperature, pressure, voltage, current and speed. The calibration facilities are established using state of the art instrumentation and traceable to national standards.
